ActYukon Act
SubjectHon. Vital O. Ouellette - Deputy Judge of the Supreme Court of Yukon ** Appointment **
PrecisOrder (1) appointing the Honourable VITAL O. OUELLETTE, former Justice of the Court of Queen’s Bench of Alberta, to be a DEPUTY JUDGE of the SUPREME COURT OF YUKON, effective April 18, 2021; and (2) fixing his remuneration and allowances in accordance with the schedule.
